Diagnostics:
  UnusedIncludes: Strict
  ClangTidy:
    Add: [readability*, bugprone*, modernize-use-nullptr, modernize-use-override, performance-*]
    Remove: [readability-static-accessed-through-instance, bugprone-easily-swappable-parameters, readability-braces-around-statements, readability-implicit-bool-conversion, readability-magic-numbers, readability-identifier-length, readability-uppercase-literal-suffix, readability-function-cognitive-complexity]
    CheckOptions:
      readability-identifier-naming.ClassCase: CamelCase
      readability-identifier-naming.ClassMethodCase: CamelCase
      readability-identifier-naming.ConstexprVariableCase: UPPER_CASE
